{
  "stem": "27507.9",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then this thing happened, which I mentioned to you before, that we went-- on one occasion, I went with my mother to eat lunch in that cantina in [POLISH] Street where we are there a few times before, and where the-- where one of the waitresses said to my mother that, your boy looks a bit-- he looks so unusual.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He looks like a Georgian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't know exactly what she meant by that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we decided not to go there after that again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, we went there on this occasion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my mother went somewhere, God knows where then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went on my own to the playground, to the children's playground, and was climbing over some climbing frames.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, suddenly, those children started coming around me, Polish children who are there in the playground, and asking me questions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from fairly innocent questions, it changed into a complete interrogation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what was my name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where did I live?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who was my father?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And who was my mother?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had, of course, answer-- although I didn't have false papers, but I had an answer to everything, because after all, we were already a bit prepared for such eventualities.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had a name, and a false name, and my father was an officer in a prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother is living somewhere here, and went to the country to buy some food, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, I even knew all the prayers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew all the Catholic prayers, et cetera, which I still know now, and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were discussing-- there was a whole group of those teenagers who were older than I, because I was, after all, nine or nine and a half.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
